### === API STATUS === ###

### Health Check
GET {{apiUrl}}/healthcheck

### === AUTH ENDPOINTS === ###

### Register
POST {{apiUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Vitor Muraoka",
    "age": 18,
    "email": "vitor.muraoka2@developz.com.br",
    "password": "vitor123"
}

### Login
POST {{apiUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "vitor.muraoka@developz.com.br",
    "password": "vitor123"
}

### Verify 2FA (login proccess)
POST {{apiUrl}}/auth/2fa/verify
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "code": "429561"
}

### Refresh Access Token
POST {{apiUrl}}/auth/refresh-access-token
Cookie: refreshToken={{refreshToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

### Enable 2FA
POST {{apiUrl}}/auth/2fa/enable
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: image/png

### Verify 2FA (setup proccess - while enabling)
POST {{apiUrl}}/auth/2fa/setup/verify
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "code": "029785"
}

### === TASK ENDPOINTS === ###

### Task List
GET {{apiUrl}}/task
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

### Specific Task
GET {{apiUrl}}/task/11
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Task Creation
POST {{apiUrl}}/task
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "title": "This task is insane!",
    "description": "LOOK AT MY NEW TASK. LET'S GO!!!",
    "dueDate": "2021-05-11"
}

### Task Update
PUT {{apiUrl}}/task/11
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "title": "Now, it's not"
}

### Task Partial Update (change status)
PATCH {{apiUrl}}/task/11
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "isDone": true
}

### Task Deletion 
DELETE {{apiUrl}}/task/9
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### === USER ENDPOINTS === ###

### User Data (for logged user)
GET {{apiUrl}}/user
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}